metadata.name: Nothing More
metadata.description:
Shades of Black NFT Collection will have 10 unique 1/1 NFT Artworks that fully investigate my young body in the most artistic manner possible. I am still experimenting a lot with both my body and photography, please do not judge to harsh :)
